Eliminate targets in each of the three antechambers before infiltrating the final chamber and engaging the cyclopean toad who makes the cave its den. Making quick work of the creature is key, for the yarzons who lurk behind the chamber's boulders will emerge once they smell blood.]],level=15,level_sync=16,name=[[Basic Training: Enemy Strongholds]],name_ja=[[全関門を突破し、最深部の敵を討て！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10004]={name_fr=[[Reconquête D'une Carapace Escamotée]],name_de=[[Gil Oder Leben]],help_en=[[Wealthy noble Teledji Adeledji has had his prized pet, a rare gil turtle, kidnapped by ruthless bandits who seek a sizable ransom for the gentle wavekin's return. Always a man of principle, Teledji Adeledji has decided that instead of caving to the bandit's demands, he will offer the ransom to anyone who can safely retrieve his pet from the clutches of evil.

After weakening the gil turtle, slay fire sprites and use their cores to light a special herb on fire. The smoke released should be powerful enough to put the creature to sleep, but only if the turtle is close enough to the flames.]],level=15,level_sync=16,name=[[Hero On The Half Shell]],name_ja=[[ギルガメを捕獲せよ！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10005]={name_fr=[[Opération Fleurs Du Mal]],name_de=[[Unkraut Jäten]],help_en=[[The forest's landtraps have reached maturity and begun releasing noisome pollen clusters in their efforts to reproduce. When taken into the lungs, the pollen can cause severe irritation, nausea, and in the case of extended exposure, even death. These vile seedkin must be dealt with before the entire Twelveswood is engulfed in a cloud of despair!]],level=20,level_sync=21,name=[[Pulling Poison Posies]],name_ja=[[有毒妖花を駆除せよ！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10006]={name_fr=[[Expédition Punitive Contre Les Ventrerouge]],name_de=[[Ins Wespennest Stechen]],help_en=[[A notorious band of outlaws known as the Redbelly Wasps is seeking to establish a new hideout near the Thousand Maws of Toto-Rak.

Once the leader is attacked, he will summon nearby allies to his aid, including powerful conjurers skilled in the arts of healing. Defeating these allies before engaging their leader will greatly increase your chance of success.]],level=20,level_sync=21,name=[[Stinging Back]],name_ja=[[無法者「似我蜂団」を撃滅せよ！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10007]={name_fr=[[Briaxio à Bras Raccourcis]],name_de=[[Briaxio Ausschalten]],help_en=[[Hostile sylphs who would rather see the Twelveswood burn before making peace with the people of Gridania have begun using their forbidden magicks to charm the forest's creatures into doing their bidding. Temporarily enhanced by the spells, these turned creatures now possess the ability to enfeeble their victims with terrible poisons and wide-reaching attacks.

Only by slaying the renegade sylph leader Briaxio of the Well will the creatures' minds be freed.]],level=25,level_sync=26,name=[[All's Well That Ends In The Well]],name_ja=[[夢幻のブラキシオを討て！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10008]={name_fr=[[Les Gobelins Bombardiers]],name_de=[[Bombige Goblins]],help_en=[[A lawless cadre of goblins has seized the Matron's Lethe, preventing passage to and from the upper reaches of the Twelveswood. Now, all those who approach are greeted with a shower of time-activated bombs tossed from behind makeshift barricades.

Slay the goblins, defeat their leader, and reclaim the area, so that travel through the forest will be safe once again.]],level=25,level_sync=26,name=[[Flicking Sticks And Taking Names]],name_ja=[[爆弾魔ゴブリン軍団を撃滅せよ！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10009]={name_fr=[[Sus Au Morbol Pollueur]],name_de=[[Tödliches Rankenspiel]],help_en=[[A massive tangle of vivified briar and vines known by the locals as Toxic Tamlyn has taken root in Fool Falls and is poisoning the water which flows into the Nym River, and eventually down to the Rhotano Sea and Limsa Lominsa. The morbol must be slain before the city-state's entire freshwater supply is contaminated, but to do so will require entering an area churning with deadly bubbles that release noisome fumes and bloodthirsty denizens of the deep.]],level=30,level_sync=31,name=[[More Than A Feeler]],name_ja=[[汚染源モルボルを討て！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10010]={name_fr=[[Buso L'immolateur]],name_de=[[Gefahr Aus Dem Nichts]],help_en=[[A terrible creature calling itself Buso has made a nearby mineshaft his new home away from the void. Slay the fiend before he can do whatever it is he came from the dark reaches of the outerworld to do.

Buso draws his power from eerie blue flames which erupt from the carcasses of minions summoned from the void and then sacrificed here in this realm. While these flames burn, Buso will be nigh indestructible. Extinguish the fires before attempting to engage him.]],level=30,level_sync=31,name=[[Annoy The Void]],name_ja=[[坑道に現れた妖異ブソを討て！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10011]={name_fr=[[Ombres Et Griffes]],name_de=[[Kampf Gegen Schatten]],help_en=[[To the east of Dragonhead, near the southern cliffs of the Sea of Clouds, a significant rift in the aether has been detected. Through this rift, a massive horned demon and a small army of its invincible minions have appeared, posing a threat to the Ishgardian knights stationed at the outposts nearby. For the time being, the creatures appear content with remaining on their rocky outcropping, but for how long they will remain is uncertain. Engage the voidsent, ignoring the incessant hounding of the minions, and focusing your efforts on their leader.]],level=35,level_sync=36,name=[[Shadow And Claw]],name_ja=[[無敵の眷属を従えし、大型妖異を討て！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10012]={name_fr=[[Longue Vie à La Reine]],name_de=[[Miss Bombastic]],help_en=[[At first, the now-frequent deadly avalanches in the Coerthas highlands were written off as displays of Oschon's might. That is, until local mountaineers spotted a giant bomb sending smaller explosives up onto the Nail to self-destruct, triggering massive cataracts of snow and rock. Knowing now the true cause of the matter, the Holy See has put a bounty on the floating head of this “bomb queen.” The task of regicide, however, will not be an easy one, for she is attended to by a retinue of royal subjects who are ready to serve her in any way necessary─including self-destruction.]],level=35,level_sync=36,name=[[Long Live The Queen]],name_ja=[[ボムを率いる「ボムクイーン」を討て！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10013]={name_fr=[[Quintettes Infernaux]],name_de=[[Unzertrennlich]],help_en=[[Five voidsent demons have descended into the Singing Shards, devouring the souls of any and all who cross their path. Early attempts at slaying the creatures have all ended in failure, for as long as one survives, it will continuously summon the fallen back to its side.

If a party were able to somehow time the killing blows necessary to fell all five of the creatures at once, victory may be possible. However, the demons will try and stop this by employing a combination of complex battle formations to thwart their pursuers' plans.]],level=40,level_sync=41,name=[[Ward Up]],name_ja=[[不気味な陣形を組む妖異をせん滅せよ！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[10014]={name_fr=[[Trinité Sinistre]],name_de=[[Wuchtige Dreifaltigkeit]],help_en=[[The gigants are made up of three distinctive classes: the ruling class of gigas, the slave class of giants, and the hecatoncheires─a second class of slaves who have spent the past several centuries trapped in a sealed mine. The enmity between the classes runs deep, and when any two converge, sparks will fly. But, when all three converge...the results can be devastating.

Parties from all three of the gigant classes have stumbled onto a dig site of the Sons of Saint Coinach. The researchers have all fled to safety, but the artifacts they discovered remain on the field. Slay the intruders while protecting the relics from needless destruction.]],level=40,level_sync=41,name=[[Solemn Trinity]],name_ja=[[三つ巴の巨人族を制し、遺物を守れ！]],content_name=[[Guildhests]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=30,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[15001]={name_fr=[[Éviter Les Attaques à Aire D'effet]],name_de=[[Flächenangriffen Ausweichen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Avoid Area Of Effect Attacks]],name_ja=[[範囲攻撃を避けよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15002]={name_fr=[[Générer De L'inimitié Avec Un Combo]],name_de=[[Mit Kombos Feindseligkeit Auf Sich Ziehen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Execute A Combo To Increase Enmity]],name_ja=[[コンボで敵視を集めよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15003]={name_fr=[[Effectuer Le Combo En Combat]],name_de=[[Kombos Im Kampf Einsetzen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Execute A Combo In Battle]],name_ja=[[実戦でコンボに挑戦しよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15004]={name_fr=[[Attirer L'inimitié De Plusieurs Ennemis Sur Soi]],name_de=[[Feindseligkeit Mehrerer Gegner Auf Sich Ziehen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Accrue Enmity From Multiple Targets]],name_ja=[[複数の敵から敵視を集めよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15005]={name_fr=[[Affronter Plusieurs Ennemis]],name_de=[[Gegen Mehrere Gegner Auf Einmal Kämpfen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Engage Multiple Targets]],name_ja=[[実戦で複数の敵と戦ってみよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15006]={name_fr=[[Générer De L'inimitié à Distance]],name_de=[[Aus Der Ferne Feindseligkeit Auf Sich Ziehen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Execute A Ranged Attack To Increase Enmity]],name_ja=[[遠距離から敵視を集めよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15007]={name_fr=[[Faire Face à Des Renforts Ennemis]],name_de=[[Feindliche Verstärkung Aufhalten]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Engage Enemy Reinforcements]],name_ja=[[敵の増援に対応しよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15008]={name_fr=[[Vaincre Un Ennemi En Assistant Des Alliés]],name_de=[[Gegner Gemeinsam Besiegen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Assist Allies In Defeating A Target]],name_ja=[[味方と協力して敵を倒そう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15009]={name_fr=[[Vaincre Un Ennemi Occupé Par Un Allié]],name_de=[[Den Gegner Eines Verbündeten Besiegen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Defeat An Occupied Target]],name_ja=[[味方が引きつけている敵を倒そう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15010]={name_fr=[[Combattre En évitant Les Attaques Ennemies]],name_de=[[Angriffen Ausweichen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Avoid Engaged Targets]],name_ja=[[敵の攻撃を避けながら戦おう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15011]={name_fr=[[Éliminer Les Renforts Ennemis]],name_de=[[Feindliche Verstärkung Aufhalten]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Engage Enemy Reinforcements]],name_ja=[[敵の増援に対応しよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15012]={name_fr=[[Interagir Avec Le Décor En Combat]],name_de=[[Mit Dem Gelände Interagieren]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Interact With The Battlefield]],name_ja=[[ギミックを活用して戦おう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15013]={name_fr=[[Soigner Un Allié]],name_de=[[Verbündete Heilen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Heal An Ally]],name_ja=[[味方を回復しよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15014]={name_fr=[[Soigner Plusieurs Alliés]],name_de=[[Mehrere Verbündete Heilen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Heal Multiple Allies]],name_ja=[[複数の味方を回復しよう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15015]={name_fr=[[Combattre En évitant Les Attaques Ennemies]],name_de=[[Angriffen Ausweichen]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Avoid Engaged Targets]],name_ja=[[敵の攻撃を避けながら戦おう！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[15016]={name_fr=[[Exercice Final]],name_de=[[Letzte Übung]],help_en=[[]],item_level_sync=5,level=15,level_sync=15,name=[[Final Exercise]],name_ja=[[最終訓練！]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[20001]={name_fr=[[Le Cratère Des Tisons]],name_de=[[Das Grab Der Lohe]],help_en=[[Owing to a betrayal, you have been captured by the Amalj'aa and taken to their stronghold of Zanr'ak, there to be given as an offering to the primal Ifrit. If you are to survive this fiery encounter with the Lord of the Inferno, you and your comrades must fight with no less than every onze of your strength. Should you fall, your souls shall burn for eternity...]],level=20,level_sync=22,name=[[The Bowl Of Embers]],name_ja=[[イフリート討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20002]={name_fr=[[Le Nombril]],name_de=[[Der Nabel]],help_en=[[Having passed the seemingly endless trials imposed upon you by the Company of Heroes, you have been entrusted with the knowledge of a secret way into the Navel, the domain of the primal Titan. Courtesy of Y'shtola's magicks, the beastman aetheryte is now primed to send you to a confrontation with the Lord of Crags. Gird your loins for a struggle of titanic proportions.]],level=34,level_sync=36,name=[[The Navel]],name_ja=[[タイタン討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20003]={name_fr=[[Hurlœil]],name_de=[[Das Tosende Auge]],help_en=[[With the aid of the Enterprise and its legendary captain, Cid Garlond, you have broken through the swirling winds that shield the Howling Eye. Yet the challenges you have surmounted pale in comparison to the one that awaits you beyond the gates. At long last, the end is nigh─be it Garuda's or your own. ]],level=44,level_sync=46,name=[[The Howling Eye]],name_ja=[[ガルーダ討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20004]={name_fr=[[Le Cratère Des Tisons (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Ifrit]],help_en=[[While your victory over the Ultima Weapon has set off waves of celebration across the land, the jubilation is short-lived, for the beast tribes are seeking to summon their gods once more. Confirmation has arrived that the Amalj'aa have already succeeded in calling forth Ifrit, who is returned far mightier than his last incarnation owing to the vast amounts of crystals he has gorged upon. Prepare yourself for a scorching encounter.]],item_level=49,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Bowl Of Embers (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真イフリート討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20005]={name_fr=[[Le Nombril (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Titan]],help_en=[[From deep within their mines, the kobolds have watched and waited for another opportunity to summon their Great Father and wreak havoc on Limsa Lominsa. With the destruction of the Ultima Weapon, the final obstacle to their plans was removed, allowing the beastmen to summon their god without fear of imperial reprisal. Once more, it falls to you to ensure that the Lord of Crags never sees the light of day.]],item_level=57,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Navel (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真タイタン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20006]={name_fr=[[Hurlœil (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Garuda]],help_en=[[Not to be outdone by the Amalj'aa, the Ixal have also taken advantage of the Ultima Weapon's destruction and again summoned their patron deity. What is worse, this most recent incarnation of Garuda is said to possess a nigh-insatiable appetite for destruction. If Coerthas and the Twelveswood are to be spared further destruction, you must return to the Howling Eye and seek an audience with the Lady of the Vortex.]],item_level=52,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Howling Eye (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真ガルーダ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20007]={name_fr=[[Le Cap Vendouest]],name_de=[[Kap Westwind]],help_en=[[It has come to light that Rhitahtyn sas Arvina, praefectus castrorum of the XIVth Legion, is scheduled to inspect the imperial outpost at Cape Westwind. Although native to a territory subjugated by the Empire, Rhitahtyn's prowess as a field tactician has won him a station of great authority within the Garlean military. Such a formidable enemy general will surely prove an obstacle to the Alliance's efforts to purge the realm of the imperial menace. For the first phase of Operation Archon, you have been entrusted the mission of infiltrating the imperial outpost and striking him down.]],level=49,level_sync=50,name=[[Cape Westwind]],name_ja=[[リットアティン強襲戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[20008]={name_fr=[[Le Cratère Des Tisons (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Ifrit]],help_en=[[Having partaken further of Ascian wisdom, the Amalj'aa have succeeded in summoning the mightiest incarnation of their god to date. Ifrit has returned amidst hellfire and brimstone, and the lizardmen bask in the heat of destruction as warriors of the Immortal Flames fall to the primal like slugs shriveling beneath the desert sun. Can a Warrior of Light prevail against such an irrepressible force?]],item_level=70,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Bowl Of Embers (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極イフリート討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20009]={name_fr=[[Le Nombril (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Titan]],help_en=[[When northern Vylbrand is racked by an earthquake, Urianger Augurelt suspects the kobolds of summoning the primal Titan. The Scion of the Seventh Dawn is proven irritatingly correct in short order when the Lord of Crags appears in the mountains of O'Ghomoro to flaunt powers even greater than were supposed. It does not take an augur to see that a battle to the death must soon follow.]],item_level=67,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Navel (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極タイタン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20010]={name_fr=[[Hurlœil (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Garuda]],help_en=[[An attack by the primal Garuda has annihilated an entire Twin Adder brigade, with the sole survivor left to tell a tale writ in terror and misery. Garuda's powers are far greater than they should be; left with few options and all but one of them almost certain failures, the Order of the Twin Adder turns to the Scions of the Seventh Dawn, so that they may summon a Warrior of Light.]],item_level=65,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Howling Eye (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極ガルーダ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20011]={name_fr=[[La Lisière De Ronces (brutal)]],name_de=[[Königliche Konfrontation (schwer)]],help_en=[[Good King Moggle Mog, the Twelfth of His Name, has once more been called forth by the Mogglesguard. Though the king is not considered a primal in the strictest sense, he poses a threat not unlike that of the beastman gods, in that his influence could corrupt his people's peaceful nature. And so, like those other aether-starved beings, he too must be felled for the sake of the realm.]],item_level=54,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Thornmarch (Hard)]],name_ja=[[善王モグル・モグXII世討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20012]={name_fr=[[La Lisière De Ronces (extrême)]],name_de=[[Königliche Konfrontation (extrem)]],help_en=[[Kuplo Kopp's attempt to chastise the Mogglesguard for their dangerous and foolhardy actions has not had the intended effect. Reminded of how deadly the Twelveswood has become, the royal guards have instead channeled their fear and desperation into calling forth an even more potent potentate. The Good King Moggle Mog XII now styles himself the Great King Moggle Mog XII, and all the evildoers in the forest shall tremble before his majestic wrath!]],item_level=80,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Thornmarch (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極王モグル・モグXII世討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[20013]={name_fr=[[Le Fléau D'Ultima]],name_de=[[Heldenlied Von Ultima]],help_en=[[Inspired by tales of your victory over the Ultima Weapon, the wandering minstrel come to Revenant's Toll has composed an epic ballad in your honor. However, as minstrels are wont to do, he has embellished certain details for dramatic effect. Although it can hardly be considered an accurate retelling, you cannot deny his skill with words, for as you listen to his melodious voice, you find yourself reliving the events of that fateful day in the Praetorium... ]],item_level=61,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Minstrel's Ballad: Ultima's Bane]],name_ja=[[究極幻想 アルテマウェポン破壊作戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20014]={name_fr=[[Défi Spécial III]],name_de=[[Event-Inhalt 3]],help_en=[[イベント用コンテンツ：3]],level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Special Event I]],name_ja=[[イベント用コンテンツ：3]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=15,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[3.0]],},},[20015]={name_fr=[[Défi Spécial I]],name_de=[[Event-Inhalt 1]],help_en=[[ ]],level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Special Event II]],name_ja=[[イベント用コンテンツ：1]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=15,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20016]={name_fr=[[Défi Spécial II]],name_de=[[Event-Inhalt 2]],help_en=[[ ]],level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Special Event III]],name_ja=[[イベント用コンテンツ：2]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=15,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.1]],},},[20017]={name_fr=[[Le Briseur De Marées (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Leviathan]],help_en=[[The Sahagin, reviled beast tribe native to the Indigo Deep, have succeeded in summoning forth their voracious god, the primal Leviathan. Should the mighty serpent be allowed to unleash a tidal wave, the entire city of Limsa Lominsa will be swept into the sea. Faced with watery oblivion, the leaders of the Maelstrom have conceived a desperate plan: by lashing together two warships and filling their holds with corrupted crystals, they hope to pierce the Lord of the Whorl's defenses and give a chosen few the chance to dispatch the primal with courage and steel. The Whorleater sits in the bay with her towing vessel, the Triumph, awaiting but the command to cast off. ]],item_level=60,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Whorleater (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真リヴァイアサン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[20018]={name_fr=[[Le Briseur De Marées (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Leviathan]],help_en=[[Though their beloved god was slain at the hands of the Warrior of Light, the Sahagin have wasted little time in mourning his passing. Drawing on the occult knowledge of the Ascians, the scaly beastmen have performed a foul ritual fueled by blood and sacrifice to bring forth the mightiest incarnation of Leviathan the realm has yet seen. Before the ocean deity can summon a tidal wave of catastrophic proportions, the Whorleater must once again set sail for open waters─and for victory.]],item_level=80,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Whorleater (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極リヴァイアサン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[20019]={name_fr=[[La Chimère Dhorme Du Coerthas]],name_de=[[Kampf Gegen Die Dhorme-Chimära]],help_en=[[There are as many theories as the dhorme chimera has heads about why the creature consumes alumina. Some say the uniquely fine alumina salts to be found in its capacious stomach are an accident of friction and heat, while others claim intent. Those such as Gerolt, who forge anew the arms of eld, have a simpler question: will you slay the fire-breathing enigma?]],item_level=52,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[A Relic Reborn: The Chimera]],name_ja=[[ドルムキマイラ討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[20020]={name_fr=[[L'hydre D'Halatali]],name_de=[[Kampf Gegen Die Hydra]],help_en=[[Left to starve in their abandoned training grounds, the fighting beasts of Halatali have survived on the flesh of the unprepared these past five years. Some have prospered more than others in the abattoir gloom; the hydra reposes fat and malignant, an apt pupil for your yet unfinished relic. Seek out this foul orphan of the Calamity, and let the bards sing of it.

※You cannot change weapons once bound by duty. Please ensure that you have equipped your unfinished relic weapon if you are undertaking this trial in order to complete the quest “A Relic Reborn.”]],item_level=52,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[A Relic Reborn: The Hydra]],name_ja=[[ハイドラ討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[20021]={name_fr=[[Affrontement Sur Le Grand Pont]],name_de=[[Duell Auf Der Großen Brücke]],help_en=[[In his quest to acquire the strongest of weapons, the notorious duelist Gilgamesh has long eluded authorities─until now. Forced to take a stand at the impassable Griffin Crossing, he has challenged you to a “duel.” Triumph, and he shall yield his latest prize. But should you fail, your weapons will be forfeit.]],item_level=50,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Battle On The Big Bridge]],name_ja=[[ギルガメッシュ討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[20022]={name_fr=[[L'Arbre Du Jugement (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Ramuh]],help_en=[[After forging deep into the Sylphlands, you meet with the intimidating guardian deity of the sylphs─the primal Ramuh. But before he will consider your proposal of peace, the Lord of Levin first demands proof that you possess the strength required to repel the Empire from the Twelveswood. The thunderous entity then vanishes in a blinding flash, leaving the words of his challenge yet echoing in your ears. Enter the primal's domain, and prepare to be measured on the scales of battle!]],item_level=65,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Striking Tree (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真ラムウ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[20023]={name_fr=[[L'Arbre Du Jugement (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Ramuh]],help_en=[[Satisfied that the Warrior of Light has passed his trial, the primal Ramuh departs Eorzea for the aetherial sea. His sylvan thralls, however, unconvinced that their territory is truly safe, have focused their deep-rooted fear and spite into summoning their god anew. Can you rise to the challenge and prove your might once again? Crackling with the vengeful energies of his children's prayers, the Lord of Levin's judgment promises to be harsh indeed...]],item_level=85,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Striking Tree (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極ラムウ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[20024]={name_fr=[[L'Amphithéâtre D'Akh Afah (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Shiva]],help_en=[[For as long as their nation has warred with Dravania, there have been Ishgardians who instead chose to ally themselves with the dragons. Shiva is said to have been among the first, hence why the heretics revere her as a saint. That Iceheart and her followers intend to summon Shiva with the crystals they have stolen is plain. But is this unprecedented act even possible? If so, then Ishgard─if not the entire realm─is in grave danger.]],item_level=80,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Akh Afah Amphitheatre (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真シヴァ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[20025]={name_fr=[[L'Amphithéâtre D'Akh Afah (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Shiva]],help_en=[[House Durendaire's efforts to establish an outpost in Snowcloak have met with disaster, owing to a surprise attack by Iceheart's followers. Now in possession of their former fortress, as well as a vast supply of crystals, the heretics are certain to summon Saint Shiva once more. If past experience is any indication, this new incarnation will be stronger than the last. Regardless, it changes nothing─ Iceheart's crusade cannot continue, and only you have the power to stop her.]],item_level=95,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Akh Afah Amphitheatre (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極シヴァ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[20026]={name_fr=[[Le Col Du Dragon]],name_de=[[Das Drachenhals-Kolosseum]],help_en=[[It's a frenetic free-for-all as the Mythril Cup moves to Halatali for the climactic confrontation! Rain will lash and winds will bluster in this perfect storm of a battle. When the tempest subsides, who will rise above the chaos to lay claim to the victor's spoils? Will it be the Warrior of Light, savior of Eorzea and champion of her people, or the dastardly duo of Ultros and Typhon!? All will be answered in Halatali, atop the Dragon's Neck!]],item_level=80,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Dragon's Neck]],name_ja=[[アマジナ杯闘技会決勝戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[20027]={name_fr=[[La Fontaine D'Urth]],name_de=[[Jenseits Urths Quelle]],help_en=[[In the moons following the Calamity, myriad rumors of ghastly creatures stalking the Twelveswood began spreading across the realm like wildfire. While most of the rumors have since been deemed unfounded, there is one series of events that has remained difficult to cast off as merely the ravings of broken-minded smallfolk: that concerning the supposed Dark Rider of the Shroud. After several deaths attributed to this mysterious figure, Seedseer O-App-Pesi sought communion with the spirits of the Twelveswood, only to learn that the rider was none other than the elder primal Odin. Slain in the Third Astral Era by an Allagan hero, why and how the primal has returned to Eorzea remains a mystery─one now in the capable hands of Eorzea's adventurers.]],item_level=95,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Urth's Fount]],name_ja=[[闘神オーディン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.38]],},},[20028]={name_fr=[[Le Siège De La Sainte Cité D'Ishgard]],name_de=[[Der Schicksalsweg]],help_en=[[The Steps of Faith─the sole means of approaching the city of Ishgard. As well as providing passage across the Sea of Clouds, this great stone bridge also serves to anchor the series of arcane wards known as Daniffen's Collar.

Long has the Holy See relied upon these barriers to shield the city from Dravanian assault, but it did not reckon upon the brazen actions of Lady Iceheart. The outermost layer of protection has been dispelled, allowing the mighty dragon Vishap to land upon the far end of the Steps of Faith. Leading an army of lesser kin, the massive creature is intent on destroying the exposed foundations of the remaining wards. Take up position alongside the Temple Knights, and defend the structure from the ravaging forces of the Horde!]],item_level=90,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Steps Of Faith]],name_ja=[[皇都イシュガルド防衛戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.55]],},},[20029]={name_fr=[[La Chrysalide]],name_de=[[Chrysalis]],help_en=[[A ruthless Ascian known as Nabriales has intruded upon the sanctum of the Scions of the Seventh Dawn, spiriting away both the Antecedent and the powerful relic she refused to yield. Pursue the Paragon through the dimensional rift and prise Minfilia─and Tupsimati─from his tenebrous grasp.]],item_level=90,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Chrysalis]],name_ja=[[アシエン・ナプリアレス討伐戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.5]],},},[20030]={name_fr=[[Revanche Au Vieux Château]],name_de=[[Revanche In Den Ruinen]],help_en=[[How many realms has he traversed, and how many rivals has he felled? Gilgamesh journeys ever onward in his unending quest for the strongest of weapons. But the road is long and lonesome, and a painted rooster─loyal and noble as the bird may be─can bring a man only so much comfort in the darkest and most trying of times. So it was that Gilgamesh turned to the heavens, pleading to be reunited with a long-lost companion. Be it by fortune or fate, his prayers were heard, and the stage for the final confrontation is set. To the victor goes the Treaty-Blade!]],item_level=90,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Battle In The Big Keep]],name_ja=[[真ギルガメッシュ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.5]],},},[20031]={name_fr=[[Thok Ast Thok (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Ravana]],help_en=[[An insectoid beast tribe connected by a hive mind, the Gnath have but one collective desire: to expand their territory and prosper without fear of dragons. It was by this simple yet powerful wish that a mighty primal bent on war and conquest was summoned into existence. Bound by your promise to Vidofnir to remove this threat to dragonkind, you must now lead your companions into battle against the savage entity known as Ravana, Lord of the Hive.]],level=53,level_sync=54,name=[[Thok Ast Thok (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真ラーヴァナ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.0]],},},[20032]={name_fr=[[Thok Ast Thok (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Ravana]],help_en=[[Willed back into existence by his zealous children, Ravana, the Lord of the Hive, is risen again with ever greater savagery. Left unchecked, the Wrath of the Colony will surely seek out the Warring Triad on Azys Lla to feed upon the sleeping eikons' strength. Heed Unukalhai's warning, and slay the entity before his insatiable appetite for power unleashes destruction of cataclysmic proportions...]],item_level=175,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Thok Ast Thok (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極ラーヴァナ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.0]],},},[20033]={name_fr=[[L'Immensité Bleue (brutal)]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Bismarck]],help_en=[[Inspiration often finds us in surprising ways. So it was that a casual mention of skyfishing helped Cid Garlond conceive a plan to lure out Bismarck, the Lord of the Mists, by using the Enterprise to tow an island through the Sea of Clouds. After binding the beast with chains fired from dragonkillers, he hopes you can engage it in the traditional fashion. Though the plan is somewhat sound in theory, there is no telling how effective it will be in practice. Nevertheless, the engineer has seen you through many dangerous situations in the past, so at least the odds are in his favor...]],level=57,level_sync=58,name=[[The Limitless Blue (Hard)]],name_ja=[[真ビスマルク討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.0]],},},[20034]={name_fr=[[L'Immensité Bleue (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Bismarck]],help_en=[[As is all too often the case, a primal you felled has once again been summoned. According to Unukalhai, the stakes are even higher this time, as Bismarck's reappearance threatens to hasten the awakening of the Warring Triad─three eikons sealed within the Aetherochemical Research Facility on Azys Lla. Fortunately, you have developed a sound method for slaying flying feathered whales. The Enterprise Excelsior and your island await.]],item_level=165,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Limitless Blue (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極ビスマルク討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.0]],},},[20035]={name_fr=[[Le Réacteur De Singularité]],name_de=[[Singularitäts-Reaktor]],help_en=[[Taking the soul of the legendary King Thordan into his flesh, the archbishop transforms into a primal before your very eyes. Sustained by a millennium of prayer and the Eye's aether, he declares his intent to rule over the world with an iron fist and for all time. Standing at his side are the sworn brothers of the Heavens' Ward, who have likewise transcended their mortal limits by becoming incarnations of the knights twelve. Strike them down, and eradicate the root of the Dragonsong War.]],item_level=142,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Singularity Reactor]],name_ja=[[ナイツ・オブ・ラウンド討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.0]],},},[20036]={name_fr=[[Le Règne De Thordan]],name_de=[[Heldenlied Von Thordans Fall]],help_en=[[With his typical flair for embellishment, the wandering minstrel has woven yet another stirring epic─this time from the threads of your Azys Lla confrontation with Archbishop Thordan VII. With the final verse yet ringing in the chambers of your mind, the memories of that titanic struggle arise once more with an almost surreal clarity...]],item_level=190,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Minstrel's Ballad: Thordan's Reign]],name_ja=[[蒼天幻想 ナイツ・オブ・ラウンド討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.1]],},},[20037]={name_fr=[[Unité De Contention S1P7]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Sephirot]],help_en=[[Sephirot, the Fiend, was a deity once worshipped by a treelike race native to Meracydia. Brought into being for the sole purpose of repelling the Allagan invasion, Sephirot inflicted ruinous losses upon the imperial army before finally being subdued and imprisoned in the central facility of Azys Lla. And now, millennia later, this immensely powerful entity threatens to awaken, his vengeful dreams disturbed by the careless ambitions of Archbishop Thordan VII. Topple the first pillar of the Warring Triad, or wheresoever his colossal shadow falls shall be visited by unthinkable catastrophe!]],item_level=190,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Containment Bay S1T7]],name_ja=[[魔神セフィロト討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[20038]={name_fr=[[Unité De Contention S1P7 (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Sephirot]],help_en=[[Preserved upon the Allagan tomestone you received from Unukalhai was an extraordinary history─a detailed record of the battles fought between the eikon Sephirot and the armies of Allag. After feeding the account of this epic conflict into Azys Lla's verification systems, you have succeeded in activating what the node describes as a “combat simulation.”

Can the enigmatic technology of the ancient empire truly manifest an enhanced simulacrum of the formidable Fiend? Can this artificial incarnation truly surpass the threat posed by the original Sephirot? There is but one way to know for certain...]],item_level=205,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Containment Bay S1T7 (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極魔神セフィロト討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[20039]={name_fr=[[La Dernière Avancée De La Foi]],name_de=[[Der Letzte Schicksalsweg]],help_en=[[Imbued with Hraesvelgr's last sliver of hope, you stand at the forefront of your allies as the last bastion against the raging shade of Nidhogg. Have you the resolve to conquer the great wyrm at the height of his power, or will Ishgard perish in fire and ruin? Here, on the battle-stricken Steps of Faith, your deeds shall decide how the final verse of a thousand-year dirge of grief and vengeance will be sung.]],item_level=205,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Final Steps Of Faith]],name_ja=[[ニーズヘッグ征竜戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.3]],},},[20040]={name_fr=[[L'ire De Nidhogg]],name_de=[[Das Lied Von Nidhoggs Letztem Ruf]],help_en=[[Scarcely had Nidhogg fallen on the Steps of Faith, when taverns across Eorzea began to rumble with the rumors of your victory. In one such establishment did you regale a certain story-starved bard with the true details of your accomplishment─a humble account that he soon expanded into a flowery ballad of heroic proportions. Even as the lilting notes fade away, your mind is carried off by recollections of a monstrous foe, writ considerably more terrifying by the wandering minstrel's exaggerated poetry...]],item_level=220,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Minstrel's Ballad: Nidhogg's Rage]],name_ja=[[極ニーズヘッグ征竜戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.3]],},},[20041]={name_fr=[[Unité De Contention P1P6]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Sophia]],help_en=[[History tells of a Meracydian nation comprised of a multitude of races, the foundations of which were built on the worship of a single deity. The “Goddess,” as she was simply known, graced the souls of her worshipers with perfect equilibrium, binding their disparate societies in gilded chains of harmony.

In the present day, she is better known as Sophia, one of the incalculably powerful eikons of the Warring Triad. And after five thousand years of imprisonment, her failed plans for vengeance once more threaten to come to fruition. Defeat the wakened thralls and slay the stirring Goddess, lest her divine “balance” bring all the world to equal ruin!]],item_level=220,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Containment Bay P1T6]],name_ja=[[女神ソフィア討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[20042]={name_fr=[[Unité De Contention P1P6 (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Sophia]],help_en=[[A new tomestone discovered by Unukalhai contains records of ancient battles with Sophia─specialized data which will enable Azys Lla's miraculous reality augmentation technologies to generate a simulacrum of the Goddess at the height of her power. Have you the strength to overcome this challenge, as the champions of Allag once did? Enter the combat simulation, and test the limits of your might!]],item_level=235,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Containment Bay P1T6 (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極女神ソフィア討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[20043]={name_fr=[[Unité De Contention Z1P9]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Zurvan]],help_en=[[Only one pillar of the Warring Triad remains: Zurvan, the Demon. Worshipped by a Meracydian race of centaur-like beings, this eikon manifested upon the physical plane as an embodiment of eternal victory. And yet, despite his godlike might, Zurvan was captured. He has languished in his Allagan-made prison now for five thousand years, his primal desire for justice swelling in magnitude with each passing millennium...

Through an unlikely alliance with the VIth Imperial Legion, you and your companions were able to prevent a catastrophic awakening orchestrated by the Demon's thralls. But your work is not yet finished. Honor the sacrifice of Regula van Hydrus, and remove the threat of Zurvan from this world once and for all!]],item_level=235,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Containment Bay Z1T9]],name_ja=[[鬼神ズルワーン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.5]],},},[20044]={name_fr=[[Unité De Contention Z1P9 (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Zurvan]],help_en=[[You hold a tomestone recovered from the research facility of Azys Lla. According to Unukalhai, this recording device contains the data required to generate a simulacrum of Zurvan at the peak of his original, unmitigated power─the final trial of a program designed to test the mightiest of Allag's elite champions. If you would subject yourself to the dangers of this ancient challenge, you need only approach the verification node and stretch forth your hand...]],item_level=250,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Containment Bay Z1T9 (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極鬼神ズルワーン討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.5]],},},[20045]={name_fr=[[La Ménagerie Royale]],name_de=[[Königliche Menagerie]],help_en=[[Shinryu, Ilberd's draconic god of vengeance, has been claimed by none other than Zenos yae Galvus, who has used his power as a Resonant to merge with the primal and bind it to his will. Transformed into a towering being of pure violence, his very existence poses a threat not only to Ala Mhigo, but to the entire world. All now falls to you and your comrades, for if you do not stop Zenos yae Galvus, no one will...]],item_level=280,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Royal Menagerie]],name_ja=[[神龍討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.0]],},},[20046]={name_fr=[[La Crique Aux Tributs]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Susano]],help_en=[[Your efforts to wreak havoc on the Isle of Zekki and draw the Red Kojin away from their imperial masters have exceeded all expectations. Unfortunately, for reasons beyond your knowing, two of the sacred treasures stored in the isle's vault “reacted” to the presence of the Yasakani-no-Magatama, summoning forth from the aether the great kami Susano─a primal by another name. How fortunate that you had the wisdom and foresight to invite several of your fellow adventurers on this journey to the Far East, and how kind they were to agree to help you torment the Red Kojin, for no single warrior, no matter how blessed or powerful, could ever hope to slay a primal on her own, despite what some wandering minstrels would have you believe.]],level=63,level_sync=64,name=[[The Pool Of Tribute]],name_ja=[[スサノオ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.0]],},},[20047]={name_fr=[[La Crique Aux Tributs (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Susano]],help_en=[[In the shadow of Kugane's renowned Mujikoza theater, you recount your clash with Susano to the wandering minstrel. Inspired by your tale, he proceeds to commit it to song, his gift for words imbuing events with an intensity you do not quite recall. Such is common practice when adapting for the stage, the minstrel explains, as your mind wanders back to the scene of battle, the verses echoing in your mind...]],item_level=300,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Pool Of Tribute (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極スサノオ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.0]],},},[20048]={name_fr=[[Émanation]],name_de=[[Götterdämmerung - Lakshmi]],help_en=[[Upon witnessing her daughter's death at the hands of Fordola and her Skulls, the Qalyana broodmother cried out to the heavens in despair...and a primal answered. Sri Lakshmi, patron deity of the Ananta, came forth from the aether, and the imperials were put to flight. Alas, the tale did not end there, for now the Qalyana demand that the Vira come and pay tribute to the goddess. And so it falls to you and your comrades to journey unto the Qalyana stronghold of Djanan Qhat, and put an end to Sri Lakshmi's dream.]],level=67,level_sync=68,name=[[Emanation]],name_ja=[[ラクシュミ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.0]],},},[20049]={name_fr=[[Émanation (extrême)]],name_de=[[Zenit Der Götter - Lakshmi]],help_en=[[In the shadow of Kugane's renowned Mujikoza theater, you recount your clash with Sri Lakshmi to the wandering minstrel. Moved to melancholy by the tragic tale, he forgoes adapting it for the stage, choosing instead to honor the memory of the departed with a verse. So vivid are the words and sorrowful the melody, you cannot help but relive the fateful encounter in your mind's eye...]],item_level=300,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Emanation (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極ラクシュミ討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.0]],},},[20050]={name_fr=[[Le Domaine De Shinryu]],name_de=[[Das Heldenlied Von Shinryu]],help_en=[[A god born of sorrow and despair. A man who lives only for death. As one they fought the Warrior of Light, and as one they fell. No words could do this titanic encounter justice...unless they come from the wandering minstrel, to whom no event is beyond improvement. As his nimble fingers pluck out the chords, his rich voice carries you to a place above the world, one that is at once familiar and foreign: Shinryu's domain.]],item_level=320,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Minstrel's Ballad: Shinryu's Domain]],name_ja=[[極神龍討滅戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,},[20051]={name_fr=[[La Clairière De Jade]],name_de=[[Seelentanz - Byakko]],help_en=[[At the heart of every auspice is a duality: the aramitama, the primal rage; and the nigimitama, the boundless calm. Byakko of the Four Lords is on the verge of being consumed by his aramitama, and should this come to pass, he will forever be no more than a feral beast. And so it falls to you and yours to face the legendary auspice in battle─to quell the madness within and save his soul!]],item_level=325,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Jade Stoa]],name_ja=[[白虎征魂戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[20052]={name_fr=[[La Clairière De Jade (extrême)]],name_de=[[Seelensturm - Byakko]],help_en=[[A devoted student of the fine arts, the wandering minstrel has recently begun studying a form of classical Hingan poetry. Duly inspired by your account of the battle for Byakko's soul, he tries his hand at one such “tanka”, seeking to capture the essence of who the auspice truly is. Even absent music, his words nevertheless have a hypnotic feeling, and you find it rather easy to recall the encounter, albeit in a more dramatic fashion...]],item_level=340,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Jade Stoa (Extreme)]],name_ja=[[極白虎征魂戦]],content_name=[[Trials]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=60,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[25001]={name_fr=[[Le Manoir Hanté]],name_de=[[Das Geisterschloss]],help_en=[[]],level=1,level_sync=1,name=[[The Haunted Manor]],name_ja=[[亡霊屋敷 ホーンテッドマナー]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[25002]={name_fr=[[La Cérémonie De La Valention]],name_de=[[Valentionzeremonie]],help_en=[[Lovers and lovers-to-be of Eorzea! In conjunction with House Valentione, the Sanctum of the Twelve is proud to bring you the Valentione's Ceremony! Put the strength of your bond to the test in two light-hearted trials, the maze-romping “Till Mog Do Us Part” and the card-flipping “Cards Beat as One.” Is your relationship destined for bliss? Or is it doomed to wither like a bad kupo nut? Register for the ceremony now and find out, kupo!

※ The organizers accept no responsibility for relationship difficulties that may result.]],level=1,level_sync=1,name=[[The Valentione's Ceremony]],name_ja=[[ヴァレンティオンセレモニー]],time_limit=30,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30001]={name_fr=[[La Tour De Cristal - Dédale Antique]],name_de=[[Kristallturm - Das Labyrinth Der Alten]],help_en=[[With the help of Cid nan Garlond, members of the expedition to the Crystal Tower have successfully penetrated the defenses of the Eight Sentinels. The ancient Allagan structure is not so easily entered, however, and the Labyrinth of the Ancients now awaits the fellowship of NOAH as they seek the ultimate prize.]],item_level=50,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Labyrinth Of The Ancients]],name_ja=[[クリスタルタワー：古代の民の迷宮]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[30002]={name_fr=[[Le Labyrinthe De Bahamut I]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 1]],help_en=[[Situated upon Vylbrand, Castrum Occidens is more akin to a research facility than a fortress. Even before its first pillar was driven into the ground, Legatus Gaius van Baelsar had ordered his people to probe the fragment of Dalamud which fell at that precise location. The impact resulted in the creation of vast caverns pervaded by corrupted crystals. Though unknown dangers lie in wait within, you must brave them all if you are to learn the truth of the Calamity.]],item_level=70,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Binding Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 1]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：邂逅編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[30003]={name_fr=[[Le Labyrinthe De Bahamut II]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2]],help_en=[[At the depth of 912 yalms, you find your path blocked by Dalamud's internal defenses. Born of advanced Allagan science, these spherical constructs are still fully functional even after eras in existence, and will seek to annihilate all intruders or be destroyed in attempt.]],item_level=73,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Binding Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 2]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：邂逅編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[30004]={name_fr=[[Le Labyrinthe De Bahamut III]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 3]],help_en=[[At the depth of 1,233 yalms, your party comes upon the fragment of Dalamud the Garleans had sought. Its true identity is the Ragnarok, a colossal starship which fell away from the lesser moon moments before Bahamut burst free of his prison over the Carteneau Flats. To reach your destination, you must venture through this relic of ancient Allag. Stay ever on your guard, for every shadow may conceal dangers.]],item_level=70,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Binding Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 3]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：邂逅編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[30005]={name_fr=[[Le Labyrinthe De Bahamut IV]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 4]],help_en=[[At 1,524 yalms below the surface, employing the Ragnarok's drive cylinder as a makeshift lift, your party proceeds toward the main bridge. Yet you must work for every yalm you gain, for Dalamud's internal defenses will not allow you to pass unmolested.]],item_level=77,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Binding Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 4]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：邂逅編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[30006]={name_fr=[[Le Labyrinthe De Bahamut V]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 5]],help_en=[[Having overcome the seemingly endless waves of hostile constructs, you and your stalwart companions continue the descent into an unknown abyss. At the depth of 1,910 yalms, you are assailed by a winged terror: an ancient dragon brought to heel by the Allagans and made to do their bidding. The trials grow ever more arduous, but you are resolved to press on for the sake of the truth.]],item_level=82,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Binding Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 5]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：邂逅編5]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.0]],},},[30007]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut I]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 1]],help_en=[[Your foray into the caverns beneath Castrum Occidens has led you to an unexpected revelation: the incomplete form of Bahamut, harbinger of the Calamity, slumbers deep within earth. Though seemingly a prisoner, the elder primal is gradually being regenerated by the massive, Ragnarok-class internment hulks that surround the unmoving entity. Alisaie reasons that if Bahamut's full restoration is to be prevented, then all three coils sustaining and repairing the dreadful being must be deactivated. Filled with new determination, you assemble a group of courageous comrades and set your sights on the fragment of Dalamud found in the North Shroud.]],item_level=90,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 1]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：侵攻編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[30008]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut II]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 2]],help_en=[[After battling your way through to the base of the colossal fragment that impales the ground in Alder Springs, your party enters the structure through an opening in its outer shell. The sight that greets you is of an endless procession of azure-lit passages, within which can be glimpsed the grotesque silhouettes of chimerical monstrosities.]],item_level=95,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 2]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：侵攻編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[30009]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut III]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 3]],help_en=[[Your party activates the coil's lift-like mechanism, and, at a depth of 3,256 yalms, arrives within the interior of the internment hulk proper. The great cavern where the elder primal Bahamut dreams is yet many thousands of yalms distant. Explore the labyrinthine passages of the Ragnarok-class starship, and secure a route into the lowest levels of the hulk.]],item_level=100,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 3]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：侵攻編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[30010]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut IV]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 4]],help_en=[[At a depth of 6,329 yalms, your exhausted yet determined fellowship enters the hulk's operations deck. An impossible scene unfolds before you, the surreal landscape bathed in a crimson glare and holding the promise of epic conflict...]],item_level=105,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 4]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：侵攻編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.25]],},},[30011]={name_fr=[[La Tour De Cristal - Tour De Syrcus]],name_de=[[Kristallturm - Der Syrcus-Turm]],help_en=[[Having secured a path through the Labyrinth of the Ancients, the fellowship of NOAH finds itself before the entrance to the Crystal Tower proper. With the aid of their new comrades, Unei and Doga, the companions succeed in opening the gate whose workings had baffled even the brightest minds among them. Upon learning that dark forces have awakened within, the fellowship decides to suspend its investigative effort in favor of sealing off the tower. You must fight your way to the apex and defeat the resurrected Emperor Xande, that Eorzea might be free of his all-consuming ambition.]],item_level=70,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[Syrcus Tower]],name_ja=[[クリスタルタワー：シルクスの塔]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[30012]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut I (sadique)]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 1 (episch)]],help_en=[[Your foray into the caverns beneath Castrum Occidens has led you to an unexpected revelation: the incomplete form of Bahamut, harbinger of the Calamity, slumbers deep within earth. Though seemingly a prisoner, the elder primal is gradually being regenerated by the massive, Ragnarok-class internment hulks that surround the unmoving entity. Alisaie reasons that if Bahamut's full restoration is to be prevented, then all three coils sustaining and repairing the dreadful being must be deactivated. Filled with new determination, you assemble a group of courageous comrades and set your sights on the fragment of Dalamud found in the North Shroud.]],item_level=105,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut (Savage) - Turn 1]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート零式：侵攻編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[30013]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut II (sadique)]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 2 (episch)]],help_en=[[After battling your way through to the base of the colossal fragment that impales the ground in Alder Springs, your party enters the structure through an opening in its outer shell. The sight that greets you is of an endless procession of azure-lit passages, within which can be glimpsed the grotesque silhouettes of chimerical monstrosities.]],item_level=105,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut (Savage) - Turn 2]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート零式：侵攻編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[30014]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut III (sadique)]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 3 (episch)]],help_en=[[Your party activates the coil's lift-like mechanism, and, at a depth of 3,256 yalms, arrives within the interior of the internment hulk proper. The great cavern where the elder primal Bahamut dreams is yet many thousands of yalms distant. Explore the labyrinthine passages of the Ragnarok-class starship, and secure a route into the lowest levels of the hulk.]],item_level=105,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut (Savage) - Turn 3]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート零式：侵攻編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[30015]={name_fr=[[Les Méandres De Bahamut IV (sadique)]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 2 - 4 (episch)]],help_en=[[At a depth of 6,329 yalms, your exhausted yet determined fellowship enters the hulk's operations deck. An impossible scene unfolds before you, the surreal landscape bathed in a crimson glare and holding the promise of epic conflict...]],item_level=105,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Second Coil Of Bahamut (Savage) - Turn 4]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート零式：侵攻編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.3]],},},[30016]={name_fr=[[L'Abîme De Bahamut I]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 3 - 1]],help_en=[[Alisaie is resolved to go through with her quest to vanquish Bahamut, though it means confronting her beloved grandfather, whom the elder primal has made his thrall. With Alphinaud's cooperation, an aetherial pathway has been established which will take your party to one of the two internment hulks that remain to be disabled. Your foray begins in northern Thanalan, at the set of Dalamud's talons situated in Raubahn's Push. Spare no preparation and expect fierce resistance.]],item_level=110,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Final Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 1]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：真成編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[30017]={name_fr=[[L'Abîme De Bahamut II]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 3 - 2]],help_en=[[At the depth of 6,835 yalms, you and your companions are greeted by a breathtaking sight: a colossal replica of Dalamud, believed to be the device which regulates Bahamut's regeneration. The structure swarms with legions of the lesser moon's internal defenses, but through it you must go if you are to reach the main bridge.]],item_level=115,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Final Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 2]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：真成編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[30018]={name_fr=[[L'Abîme De Bahamut III]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 3 - 3]],help_en=[[At 8,872 yalms below the surface, your party arrives within Bahamut's cavernous regeneration chamber. As Alisaie moves to disable the internment hulk, she finds her way barred by her grandsire, the Archon Louisoix. The man once gave his life that the realm might be spared; if you would honor his legacy, you must now strike him down.]],item_level=120,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Final Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 3]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：真成編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[30019]={name_fr=[[L'Abîme De Bahamut IV]],name_de=[[Verschlungene Schatten 3 - 4]],help_en=[[Restored to his senses in defeat, Louisoix uses his final moments to send your party to the main bridge of the final internment hulk, there to banish Bahamut once and for all. Yet though the end of your arduous journey is in sight, doubt not but that the cornered primal will lash out with his unbridled rage. If you are to overcome this terrible foe, you and yours must be of one purpose. Join now your hearts and minds, and sally forth to bring the Seventh Umbral Era to its true conclusion─for the future of Eorzea!]],item_level=123,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The Final Coil Of Bahamut - Turn 4]],name_ja=[[大迷宮バハムート：真成編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[2.4]],},},[30020]={name_fr=[[La Tour De Cristal - Monde Des Ténèbres]],name_de=[[Die Welt Der Dunkelheit]],help_en=[[In the twilight of his reign, the first and last emperor of Allag, Xande, desired power above all else. He turned to the terrible being known as the Cloud of Darkness, a ruler of the void, and asked of her strength to make the world kneel before his throne with a covenant of blood.

When Xande was slain, his ambitions were laid to rest alongside him. Yet the Cloud of Darkness still seeks to enter the material realm, and will soon find passage through the voidgate set to manifest within Syrcus Tower. With the fiend's coming, can the fellowship of NOAH brave the void and rescue the three souls able to stem the Cloud's flood of shadows, or will the expedition itself vanish beyond the rift in the World of Darkness?]],item_level=90,level=50,level_sync=50,name=[[The World Of Darkness]],name_ja=[[クリスタルタワー：闇の世界]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[2.5]],},},[30021]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poing Du Père]],name_de=[[Alexander - Faust Des Vaters]],help_en=[[Since the Sharlayan exodus, a structure has stood steady against the flow of the Thaliak River. Now, the Illuminati have summoned a primal around this rusting ruin─a terrible colossus of steam and metal. Steel screamed against steel when it rose from the waters, and it drank deep of the land's aether before grinding again to a halt.

The voices of Idyllshire cry out, asking for aid ere their homes are crushed under the weight of iron. You must lead a band of valiant adventurers into the machina and discover how to destroy the core─lest the giant screeches again to life, and bleeds all the realm dry.]],item_level=170,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Fist Of The Father]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：起動編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.01]],},},[30022]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poignet Du Père]],name_de=[[Alexander - Elle Des Vaters]],help_en=[[In your last foray into the giant's mighty arm, you narrowly escaped Quickthinx Allthoughts and the Illuminati with your life. Yet in so doing, you won a cryptic name─Alexander. Whatever this may be, your path leads into the gloom of Gordias. March onwards with courage, for it is only in the darkness that you can learn how to stop the iron colossus.]],item_level=170,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Cuff Of The Father]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：起動編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.01]],},},[30023]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Bras Du Père]],name_de=[[Alexander - Arm Des Vaters]],help_en=[[In the Enigma Codex are writ the designs for a walking citadel. It was known as Alexander, a self-sufficient bastion for logic and reason and a beacon of knowledge for a world adrift─so says the treasure hunter Mide. The Illuminati dreamed this century-old dream, and in so doing gave form to their primal. Yet no matter how beautiful an ideal, the reality of fanatics with such power is a tarnished, ugly thing. By your hand must this threat be stopped.]],item_level=170,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Arm Of The Father]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：起動編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.01]],},},[30024]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Fardeau Du Père]],name_de=[[Alexander - Last Des Vaters]],help_en=[[The Illuminati would see the lofty ideals of the Enigma Codex turned into warped elitism, and have their primal play host to their chosen few. From within its walls, they would control the world with cold logic, and crush opposition with a fist of iron. With your eyes opened to the goblin scholars' true ambitions, you must make your way farther past the pumping pistons and grinding gears of the colossus. Can you and your comrades destroy the core therein, or will you fall and so allow your foes to wreak ruin across the realm?]],item_level=170,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Burden Of The Father]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：起動編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.01]],},},[30025]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poing Du Père (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Faust Des Vaters (episch)]],help_en=[[What fun is there in merely restating the facts? Never one to be content with the truth, the wandering minstrel has taken the liberty of retelling the tale of your journey into Alexander with his trademark embellishments. Some may question the value of such entertainment, but none can deny the skill with which he weaves his tapestry of song and verse, immersing you in memory...]],item_level=190,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Fist Of The Father (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：起動編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.05]],},},[30026]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poignet Du Père (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Elle Des Vaters (episch)]],help_en=[[What fun is there in merely restating the facts? Never one to be content with the truth, the wandering minstrel has taken the liberty of retelling the tale of your journey into Alexander with his trademark embellishments. Some may question the value of such entertainment, but none can deny the skill with which he weaves his tapestry of song and verse, immersing you in memory...]],item_level=195,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Cuff Of The Father (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：起動編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.05]],},},[30027]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Bras Du Père (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Arm Des Vaters (episch)]],help_en=[[What fun is there in merely restating the facts? Never one to be content with the truth, the wandering minstrel has taken the liberty of retelling the tale of your journey into Alexander with his trademark embellishments. Some may question the value of such entertainment, but none can deny the skill with which he weaves his tapestry of song and verse, immersing you in memory...]],item_level=200,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Arm Of The Father (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：起動編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.05]],},},[30028]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Fardeau Du Père (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Last Des Vaters (episch)]],help_en=[[What fun is there in merely restating the facts? Never one to be content with the truth, the wandering minstrel has taken the liberty of retelling the tale of your journey into Alexander with his trademark embellishments. Some may question the value of such entertainment, but none can deny the skill with which he weaves his tapestry of song and verse, immersing you in memory...]],item_level=205,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Burden Of The Father (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：起動編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.05]],},},[30029]={name_fr=[[L'Arche Du Néant]],name_de=[[Die Nichts-Arche]],help_en=[[In an age when the miracle of the airship has become commonplace, the heavens have seen the rise of a new breed of fortune hunter─the “sky pirate.” These airborne buccaneers sail the endless Sea of Clouds in search of hidden lands to explore and forgotten treasures to plunder.

At the behest of one such band of sky pirates, you have joined an expedition set on boarding the ominous ghost ship of recent rumor. Will you return triumphant with Leofard and his Redbills, arms laden with the spoils of some ancient trove, or will you fall to the perils of the haunted vessel as has every would-be looter before you...?]],item_level=175,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Void Ark]],name_ja=[[魔航船ヴォイドアーク]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[3.1]],},},[30030]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poing Du Fils]],name_de=[[Alexander - Faust Des Sohnes]],help_en=[[Although you succeeded in destroying the core of Gordias, it seems that was only a temporary measure. The walking fortress has stirred once more, and its left arm now rests on the banks of the Thaliak. The entrance lies open and unguarded, suggesting the goblins inside are as surprised as you. Take advantage of your enemy's unreadiness and face the Illuminati threat once more─hopefully for the last time.]],item_level=200,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Fist Of The Son]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：律動編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30031]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poignet Du Fils]],name_de=[[Alexander - Elle Des Sohnes]],help_en=[[Upon returning from Midas, you learn that Mide surrendered the precious fragment of the Enigma Codex to the Illuminati, and that she was in fact a surviving member of a group of Au Ra that failed to summon Alexander three years ago. Although there is certainly more to the apparent treachery than meets the eye, there is no time for doubt. Your offensive against the Illuminati must continue!]],item_level=200,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Cuff Of The Son]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：律動編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30032]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Bras Du Fils]],name_de=[[Alexander - Arm Des Sohnes]],help_en=[[You press further into the depths of the primal, and return to be greeted by Mide, who confesses that while the story of her past is true, the “fragment” she handed over to the Illuminati was nothing more than a useless rock. Not all is well, however, as Wedge informs you of Roundrox's capture by the Illuminati. Your objective is now clear─press further into Midas, and rescue the innocent goblin from her captors!]],item_level=200,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Arm Of The Son]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：律動編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30033]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Fardeau Du Fils]],name_de=[[Alexander - Last Des Sohnes]],help_en=[[You have delved into the deepest parts of Midas, and its power source lies but a short distance ahead. For the sake of Idyllshire, and Roundrox, you must disable the core before Alexander awakes to wreak havoc on the realm. Your allies stand at the ready─steel yourself to break through the Illuminati's last line of defense.]],item_level=200,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Burden Of The Son]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：律動編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30034]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poing Du Fils (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Faust Des Sohnes (episch)]],help_en=[[Sometimes even the most thrilling tale can benefit from slight embellishment, and the wandering minstrel's reimagining of your foray into Midas─while stretching the bounds of believability─proves to be even more invigorating than your memory of it. A memory you must relive in order to compare...]],item_level=215,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Fist Of The Son (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：律動編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30035]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Poignet Du Fils (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Elle Des Sohnes (episch)]],help_en=[[Sometimes even the most thrilling tale can benefit from slight embellishment, and the wandering minstrel's reimagining of your foray into Midas─while stretching the bounds of believability─proves to be even more invigorating than your memory of it. A memory you must relive in order to compare...]],item_level=220,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Cuff Of The Son (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：律動編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30036]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Bras Du Fils (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Arm Des Sohnes (episch)]],help_en=[[Sometimes even the most thrilling tale can benefit from slight embellishment, and the wandering minstrel's reimagining of your foray into Midas─while stretching the bounds of believability─proves to be even more invigorating than your memory of it. A memory you must relive in order to compare...]],item_level=225,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Arm Of The Son (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：律動編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30037]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Fardeau Du Fils (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Last Des Sohnes (episch)]],help_en=[[Sometimes even the most thrilling tale can benefit from slight embellishment, and the wandering minstrel's reimagining of your foray into Midas─while stretching the bounds of believability─proves to be even more invigorating than your memory of it. A memory you must relive in order to compare...]],item_level=225,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Burden Of The Son (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：律動編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.2]],},},[30038]={name_fr=[[La Cité Défendue De Mhach]],name_de=[[Die Stadt Der Tränen]],help_en=[[Deep in the Yafaem Saltmoor lie the ruins of the fabled city of Mhach─a civilization of the Fifth Astral Era whose prosperity was built upon unparalleled magicks of destruction. It is to this ancient edifice, and its vaults of occult secrets, that you and the Redbills plan your next foray.

You expect to encounter voidsent─the same terrible beings that grounded Radlia and her crew─but on your path to retrieve a relic of incalculable power, can you prevail over the unfettered miseries of the Weeping City itself?]],item_level=205,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[The Weeping City Of Mhach]],name_ja=[[禁忌都市マハ]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[3.3]],},},[30039]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Les Yeux Du Créateur]],name_de=[[Alexander - Augen Des Schöpfers]],help_en=[[Raised from the waters by the thrice-mad Illuminati, the steel colossus Alexander yet towers over the Thaliak, bleeding the hinterlands dry with a thirst for aether that will not be slaked. The time has come for action. As Y'shtola and Master Matoya seek to magically sever the primal's death grip on the land, you will take to the skies with Cid in hopes of securing an ingress through the colossus's mighty pate. The realm itself cries out for succor─will you rise to answer its call?]],item_level=230,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Eyes Of The Creator]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：天動編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30040]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Souffle Du Créateur]],name_de=[[Alexander - Atem Des Schöpfers]],help_en=[[History itself stands in the balance as the steel colossus is revealed to have the inconceivable power to transport its occupants through time and space, a power which the Illuminati are all too eager to use to rewrite the past and remake the future in their own twisted image. With time quite literally of the essence, you must find passage to the very heart of the colossus, where the unfortunate Roundrox─the key to Quickthinx's dark plot─is being held captive. Once more unto the breach, Warrior of Light!]],item_level=230,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Breath Of The Creator]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：天動編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30041]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Cœur Du Créateur]],name_de=[[Alexander - Herz Des Schöpfers]],help_en=[[Heeding Roundrox's innocent words, Alexander spreads forth its wings of time, swooping you and your bewildered companions three years into the past. There, you witness with your own eyes─and, in a shocking turn of events, help to bring about by your own hand─the tragedy that befell Mide and her companions that fateful day. Is time truly naught but a circle─the past, present, and future long since preordained─as the mad goblin prophet would have you believe? In the face of daunting odds, you press onward, that you might yet seize control of your own destiny.]],item_level=230,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Heart Of The Creator]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：天動編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30042]={name_fr=[[Alexander - L'Âme Du Créateur]],name_de=[[Alexander - Seele Des Schöpfers]],help_en=[[As the crystalline heart of the primal swells ever greater, its thirst for power unquenchable, your only hope lies in calling upon the knowledge of the Enigma Codex to cut off the flow of aether to the colossus's core. So it is that you and your companions must make a final, brave foray into the belly of the great steel beast. Yet your path will not be an easy one, for the Illuminati mastermind Quickthinx has promised that your next journey to the core will be your last. Who will be judged worthy of inheriting the future, and who will be cast aside as a forgotten afterthought to history? Your final confrontation with the Illuminati is at hand!]],item_level=230,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Soul Of The Creator]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー：天動編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30043]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Les Yeux Du Créateur (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Augen Des Schöpfers (episch)]],help_en=[[None can deny the wandering minstrel's inimitable way with words, nor the manner in which his penchant for embellishment and exaggeration has rendered your triumph over the primal Alexander all the more triumphant─and the insurmountable odds over which you did prevail all the more insurmountable. Reach back into your memory and relive your adventure inside the steel giant as it will live on in the hearts and minds of all who hear the tale!]],item_level=245,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Eyes Of The Creator (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：天動編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30044]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Souffle Du Créateur (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Atem Des Schöpfers (episch)]],help_en=[[None can deny the wandering minstrel's inimitable way with words, nor the manner in which his penchant for embellishment and exaggeration has rendered your triumph over the primal Alexander all the more triumphant─and the insurmountable odds over which you did prevail all the more insurmountable. Reach back into your memory and relive your adventure inside the steel giant as it will live on in the hearts and minds of all who hear the tale!]],item_level=250,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Breath Of The Creator (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：天動編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30045]={name_fr=[[Alexander - Le Cœur Du Créateur (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Herz Des Schöpfers (episch)]],help_en=[[None can deny the wandering minstrel's inimitable way with words, nor the manner in which his penchant for embellishment and exaggeration has rendered your triumph over the primal Alexander all the more triumphant─and the insurmountable odds over which you did prevail all the more insurmountable. Reach back into your memory and relive your adventure inside the steel giant as it will live on in the hearts and minds of all who hear the tale!]],item_level=255,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Heart Of The Creator (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：天動編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30046]={name_fr=[[Alexander - L'Âme Du Créateur (sadique)]],name_de=[[Alexander - Seele Des Schöpfers (episch)]],help_en=[[None can deny the wandering minstrel's inimitable way with words, nor the manner in which his penchant for embellishment and exaggeration has rendered your triumph over the primal Alexander all the more triumphant─and the insurmountable odds over which you did prevail all the more insurmountable. Reach back into your memory and relive your adventure inside the steel giant as it will live on in the hearts and minds of all who hear the tale!]],item_level=255,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Alexander - The Soul Of The Creator (Savage)]],name_ja=[[機工城アレキサンダー零式：天動編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[3.4]],},},[30047]={name_fr=[[Dun Scaith]],name_de=[[Dun Scaith]],help_en=[[The ancient tome recovered by Captain Radlia of the Talons tells of a floating refuge─an island created by Mhachi sorcerers to provide safe haven from calamitous floodwaters. With the disaster that befell the Void Ark, however, the island's intended residents never arrived. Cait Sith is convinced that Diabolos has instead claimed this refuge as his own, transforming what was to be a bastion of hope into a voidsent nest of shadowy nightmare. And it is into this fiendish lair that you must delve.

The Lady Radlia stands ready to bear you across the skies. Assault the island, reclaim the Nullstone, and cast your demonic foes into oblivion!]],item_level=235,level=60,level_sync=60,name=[[Dun Scaith]],name_ja=[[影の国ダン・スカー]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,patch={number=[[3.5]],},},[30049]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V1.0]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 1.0]],help_en=[[In your hunt for the elusive Omega, you and your comrades find yourselves unwitting subjects in its fiendish experiment. With no recourse but to do as bid, you resolve to venture into the Deltascape to do battle against unknown foes. Before you looms the test world, the image of a mysterious castle framed within its egg-like contour...]],item_level=295,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V1.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：デルタ編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.01]],},},[30050]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V2.0]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 2.0]],help_en=[[You have triumphed in your maiden encounter within the Deltascape, but there are more tests to come, each bound to be more trying than the last. According to Nero's analysis, your next opponent is capable of manipulating gravity, and by way of a countermeasure, he sends you off with one of his curious contraptions: an anti-gravity gimbal.]],item_level=295,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V2.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：デルタ編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.01]],},},[30051]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V3.0]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 3.0]],help_en=[[Fresh from your victory over the grotesque Catastrophe, you set your sights upon the next battle. Your foe is a being named Halicarnassus, an antagonist from a classical novel, wherein she rules as the Queen of Dimension Castle. Yet be it born of fact or fiction, the struggle ahead promises to be very real.]],item_level=295,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V3.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：デルタ編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.01]],},},[30052]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V4.0]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 4.0]],help_en=[[And so you come to the final encounter in the Deltascape. Awaiting you is yet another villain from a work of fiction known as Exdeath, who is described as an evil tree that assumes the form of a dark mage. Doubt not but that this will be your toughest test yet, but overcome it you must if you are to head off Omega's threat.]],item_level=295,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V4.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：デルタ編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.01]],},},[30053]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V1.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 1.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[Taken by curiosity, you activate something called the Savage Initiative at a Garlond Ironworks terminal. Apparently a program to address work-related stress, you are treated to a soothing song composed by a certain minstrel, its lush strains massaging your mind and adding vibrant flourishes to the memories of your trials within the Deltascape...]],item_level=310,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V1.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：デルタ編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.05]],},},[30054]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V2.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 2.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[Taken by curiosity, you activate something called the Savage Initiative at a Garlond Ironworks terminal. Apparently a program to address work-related stress, you are treated to a soothing song composed by a certain minstrel, its lush strains massaging your mind and adding vibrant flourishes to the memories of your trials within the Deltascape...]],item_level=315,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V2.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：デルタ編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.05]],},},[30055]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V3.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 3.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[Taken by curiosity, you activate something called the Savage Initiative at a Garlond Ironworks terminal. Apparently a program to address work-related stress, you are treated to a soothing song composed by a certain minstrel, its lush strains massaging your mind and adding vibrant flourishes to the memories of your trials within the Deltascape...]],item_level=320,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V3.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：デルタ編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.05]],},},[30056]={name_fr=[[Deltastice V4.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Deltametrie 4.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[Taken by curiosity, you activate something called the Savage Initiative at a Garlond Ironworks terminal. Apparently a program to address work-related stress, you are treated to a soothing song composed by a certain minstrel, its lush strains massaging your mind and adding vibrant flourishes to the memories of your trials within the Deltascape...]],item_level=320,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Deltascape V4.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：デルタ編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.05]],},},[30057]={name_fr=[[L'Abîme Infini De Bahamut (fatal)]],name_de=[[Endlose Schatten Von Bahamut (fatal)]],help_en=[[There once were brave souls who uncovered the truth of the Seventh Umbral Calamity. Such trials as they overcame were not to be recorded in history, but far from fading with the passage of time, they have been imagined in vivid detail by the wandering minstrel. As his lilting melody caresses your mind's eye, you cannot help but be transported to the scene of struggle against the elder primal Bahamut...]],item_level_sync=345,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Unending Coil Of Bahamut (Ultimate)]],name_ja=[[絶バハムート討滅戦]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=2,},[30058]={name_fr=[[La Cité Royale De Rabanastre]],name_de=[[Rabanastre]],help_en=[[Recently, residents of Kugane woke to find hovering above their city an airship unlike any ever seen. Yet while of Garlean design, the vessel distinctly lacked the bleak outfitting common in the Empire’s warmachina. No, this was the Prima Vista, private stage for the Majestic Imperial Theater Company─a troupe having won acclaim across Garlemald for their timeless work, The Zodiac Brave Story. Which begets the question...why are they here? The answer to that question and more lies in the selfsame legend of which they sing. The legend of Ivalice.]],item_level=305,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[The Royal City Of Rabanastre]],name_ja=[[失われた都 ラバナスタ]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=5,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=1,},[30059]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V1.0]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 1.0]],help_en=[[You are once more summoned to Omega's rift between dimensions, this time to conquer the denizens of the Sigmascape. With no spatial anchor to help pinpoint the correct segment of data, you are forced to enter the first battle bereft of any insightful analysis. Senses straining and nerves taut, you could swear you hear a high-pitched whistle echoing within the arena beyond...]],item_level=325,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V1.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：シグマ編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30060]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V2.0]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 2.0]],help_en=[[Chadarnook. According to Cid and Nero's research, such is the name given to your next devilish opponent. Had you not just won a battle against a spectral train, you might think the idea of a haunted painting absurd. Thankful for the inventive genius of your companions, you go forth armed with the Chocobo Brush─a tool specifically designed to help you overcome this bizarre encounter.]],item_level=325,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V2.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：シグマ編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30061]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V3.0]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 3.0]],help_en=[[Known simply as the “Guardian,” this foe is described by Cid as the machine responsible for defending a capital city. As a creation of otherworldly engineering it is impossible to know exactly what weapons it will bring to bear─only that this will be a contest of force versus overwhelming brute force.]],item_level=325,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V3.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：シグマ編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30062]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V4.0]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 4.0]],help_en=[[The looming face of the Sigmascape, “Kefka” will be your final opponent in this test world. Analysis of his data reveals that, despite his comical appearance, this cackling jester once rose to godhood and cast his entire planet into ruin. His is a power not to be underestimated. Nero has also alerted you to the villain's propensity for trickery, and promised to watch for deadly feints through his enhanced monitor. You can only hope that his warnings come in time...]],item_level=325,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V4.0]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ：シグマ編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30063]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V1.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 1.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[The urge to flip switches is almost irresistible...even when you know full well the consequences for doing so. Once more your finger moves as if of its own accord, and activates the second phase of the Savage Initiative. As the gentle arrangement drifts from the terminal, you are transported to a remembered vista of the Sigmascape, each lapping wave of the song swelling the boundary of your memories... ]],item_level=340,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V1.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：シグマ編1]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30064]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V2.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 2.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[The urge to flip switches is almost irresistible...even when you know full well the consequences for doing so. Once more your finger moves as if of its own accord, and activates the second phase of the Savage Initiative. As the gentle arrangement drifts from the terminal, you are transported to a remembered vista of the Sigmascape, each lapping wave of the song swelling the boundary of your memories... ]],item_level=345,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V2.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：シグマ編2]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30065]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V3.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 3.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[The urge to flip switches is almost irresistible...even when you know full well the consequences for doing so. Once more your finger moves as if of its own accord, and activates the second phase of the Savage Initiative. As the gentle arrangement drifts from the terminal, you are transported to a remembered vista of the Sigmascape, each lapping wave of the song swelling the boundary of your memories... ]],item_level=350,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V3.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：シグマ編3]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=90,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[30066]={name_fr=[[Sigmastice V4.0 (sadique)]],name_de=[[Sigmametrie 4.0 (episch)]],help_en=[[The urge to flip switches is almost irresistible...even when you know full well the consequences for doing so. Once more your finger moves as if of its own accord, and activates the second phase of the Savage Initiative. As the gentle arrangement drifts from the terminal, you are transported to a remembered vista of the Sigmascape, each lapping wave of the song swelling the boundary of your memories... ]],item_level=350,level=70,level_sync=70,name=[[Sigmascape V4.0 (Savage)]],name_ja=[[次元の狭間オメガ零式：シグマ編4]],content_name=[[Raids]],dps_per_party=4,healers_per_party=2,time_limit=120,tanks_per_party=2,patch={number=[[4.2]],},},[40008]={name_fr=[[The Feast (4x4/entraînement)]],name_de=[[The Feast (4 Gegen 4, Übungskampf)]],help_en=[[The table is set, and the wolves gather for the Feast! Will you gorge on the flesh of your foes, or find yourself served on a platter? Only the most savage of beasts are invited to this banquet─you'll need fangs of steel and an endless thirst for blood! Wait not for the tolling of the culling bell! Devour your rivals, take their hides for trophies, and build a hunter's throne from their bones!]],level=30,level_sync=70,name=[[The Feast (4 On 4 - Training)]],name_ja=[[ザ・フィースト (4対4 / カジュアルマッチ)]],content_name=[[PvP]],dps_per_party=2,healers_per_party=1,time_limit=6,tanks_per_party=1,},[40010]={name_fr=[[The Feast (4x4/classé)]],name_de=[[The Feast (4 Gegen 4, Gewertet)]],help_en=[[The table is set, and the wolves gather for the Feast! Will you gorge on the flesh of your foes, or find yourself served on a platter? Only the most savage of beasts are invited to this banquet─you'll need fangs of steel and an endless thirst for blood! Wait not for the tolling of the culling bell! Devour your rivals, take their hides for trophies, and build a hunter's throne from their bones!

